#rhinestoneart #fyp #explorepage #makeup #creativemakeup #meninmakeup #reelsinstagram #pinkhair #glossylips

It was January, just before Paris Couture Week, and I found myself partially involved in shaping some of the major looks that would later make waves on the runway. It’s an absolute privilege to work with @maccosmeticsindia @maccosmetics thats so deeply invested in artistry, one that constantly pushes boundaries and redefines beauty.

In preparation for the show, I rushed to @gauravguptaofficial ‘s office for look tests, my creative soul instantly ignited by the vision taking shape. Watching @marieke_thibaut key the looks with such precision and artistry was nothing short of inspiring. And with @saikatchakrabortyyy ‘s invaluable insights,I refined my approach, absorbing every bit of wisdom to elevate my craft.

“Across the Flame” was more than just a collection - it was a story of resilience, transformation, and cosmic energy. It spoke of strength in vulnerability, the wisdom of the stars, and the light that emerges from even the darkest flames.

And so, here’s my interpretation, my love letter to the creative wave - where Third Eye, Crystal Face, and Blue Face merge into a singular, transcendent vision. 💙

#pfw25 #maccosmetics #couturefashion #makeup #transformation #meninmakeup #creativeart #universe #blueflame #cosmic #gauravguptacouture

Yesterday was a moment of stillness before the magic came alive at Harper’s Bazaar LuXperiences. a heartfelt tribute to the legendary Rohit Bal. The evening was a celebration of creativity, artistry, and style, all converging to honor his unforgettable legacy. Every detail, meticulously captured, stood as a testament to his timeless impact on fashion. Working backstage for this extraordinary event was an incredible experience, a true privilege to contribute to a tribute befitting the brilliance of Rohit Bal.
